headline: Between Costco and Home Depot, What Is the Top Retail Stock to Buy Right Now?
summary: Costco (NASDAQ: COST) and Home Depot (NYSE: HD) are two leading retailers that investors are surely familiar with.  Costco's financial performance shows that it can succeed regardless of external factors.  This was at least the 10th straight year that Costco posted a positive figure.

headline: The Home Depot Introduces Magic Apron, a Suite of Advanced AI Tools to Help Customers with their Home Improvement Needs
summary: The Home Depot®, the world's leading home improvement retailer, is rolling out Magic Apron, a proprietary suite of generative AI tools that helps customers answer how-to and product questions and assists them with their home improvement projects. Just in time for its busy spring selling season, Magic Apron is available 24/7 to assist with detailed questions for any spring product, project and beyond.
